Package fr.inria.atlanmod.mogwai.processor

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractATLProcessor<Q extends MogwaiQuery>
    An ATL-based processor that uses an internal ATL transformation to create the GremlinScript to compute.
    AbstractQueryProcessor<Q extends MogwaiQuery>
    Provides an abstract API to process a MogwaiQuery.
    ATLQueryProcessor
    An ATL-based processor that computes a ATLQuery.
    GremlinQueryProcessor
    A simple processor that executes a GremlinQuery.
    GremlinScriptRunner
    Utility class that computes a Gremlin script and returns the raw results.
    OCLQueryProcessor
    An ATL-based processor that computes a OCLQuery.
